Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,tatakai wa yukue shirazu\NNo matter where the battle may take me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ashita to kinou no kousaten de\NAt the intersection of tomorrow and yesterday
