Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,sekai ga kuchihatetemo\NEven if the world crumbles apart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:50.40,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}世界が朽ち果てても 変わることの無いものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,kawaru koto no nai mono ga aru\NThere are things which will never change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,namida wo koraete demo\NEven as we bear tears in our eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:56.15,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}涙を堪えてでも 守るべきものが僕らにはある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,mamorubeki mono ga bokura ni wa aru\NThere are things we must protect
