Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.73,opj-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an2}遅れまいと メッセージが絶えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,message ga tainai de\NFor thousands and millions of years,
